<iframe allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" frameborder="0" height="415" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/398866238?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0" width="740"></iframe>
<p> </p>
<p>D.C. Virgo Preparatory Academy is a K-8 year-round public school that was opened by UNCW in July 2018.  The school offers a family-friendly environment, with a focus on the whole child and opportunities that extend to the UNCW campus and broader community. <em>D.C. Virgo, where families come to school together!</em></p>
<p>A few highlights:</p>
<ul>
<li>Experienced and qualified teaching staff, committed to student success;</li>
<li>Community partners who help serve the whole child;</li>
<li>Action-based learning engagement, where movement and learning go together;</li>
<li>Athletic and academic enrichment opportunities.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong> Open House Events</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Open house events have been canceled.</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
